#### Deployment vs StatefulSet ####

Deployment: Imagine three replicas.

nginx-78bc56
nginx-9ab123
nginx-ef2345

@@ Delete one Pod.

nginx-a92d88

Deployment will create New Pod with New Name and New Identity.

@@ Perfect for: Frontend, Backend, REST API, Microservices


StatefulSet: Create three replicas.

mysql-0
mysql-1
mysql-2

@@ Delete:
mysql-1

@@ Kubernetes recreates:
mysql-1

Exactly the same identity.

@@ Why not use Deployment for MySQL?
=> Deployment does not provide Stable Identity, Stable Hostname, Stable Storage and Ordered Deployment.


